# Brackle Blightwerth

Description: Male. Dressed in a weathered, though oddly scholarly attire.
Location: Sanctuary, Talenta Plains
Mannerisms: Wanders in and out of town, making odd declarations about the world. No one knows much about him otherwise, and he doesn’t respond if spoken to directly.
Motivation: Knowledge
Quote / Flavor: "A dirty, old gnome wearing torn clothes climbs onto a table, and a hush falls over the rowdy tavern. Someone whispers, “Brackle’s gonna talk” in an awed tone."
Race: Gnome
Role: Dragon Prophet
Status: Alive